Ventral tube with 4+4 apical setae and 2+2 basal setae (
Fig. 40
). Abd. II, III and IV with 17–18, 20–22, and 24–26 ventral setae respectively. Female genital plate with 6+6 pregenital setae, 3 circumgenital setae, one pair of eugenital setae and 2 pairs of post-genital setae.

